<html>
<head>
  <title>Help & FAQ</title>
  <%- include('partials/header1.ejs') %>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar1.ejs') %>

<div class="container mt-5 mb-5">

  <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Help & FAQ ‚ùì</h2>
  <p class="text-center text-muted mb-5">
    Find quick answers to common questions about PlantCare.
  </p>

  <!-- FAQ SECTION -->
  <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">

    <!-- Q1 -->
    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h2 class="accordion-header" id="q1">
        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#answer1">
          What is PlantCare?
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div id="answer1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          PlantCare connects <strong>plant owners</strong> with trusted <strong>plant sitters</strong> 
          who help with watering, sunlight, and basic plant maintenance during busy days or travel.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Q2 -->
    <div class="accordion-item mt-2">
      <h2 class="accordion-header" id="q2">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#answer2">
          How do I join as a Plant Sitter or Owner?
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div id="answer2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          Simply go to the <a href="/join-now">Join Now</a> page and choose your role during sign-up.  
          You will be redirected to a personalized experience depending on your selection.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Q3 -->
    <div class="accordion-item mt-2">
      <h2 class="accordion-header" id="q3">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#answer3">
          Is the service free?
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div id="answer3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          Yes! Creating an account and connecting with sitters/owners is free.  
          In the future, premium features may be added but the basic service will remain free.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Q4 -->
    <div class="accordion-item mt-2">
      <h2 class="accordion-header" id="q4">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#answer4">
          How does matching work?
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div id="answer4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          Matches are based on location, availability, the type of plants, and sitter experience.  
          Owners can browse sitters nearby, and sitters can view open requests.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Q5 -->
    <div class="accordion-item mt-2">
      <h2 class="accordion-header" id="q5">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#answer5">
          What if I need help with something else?
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div id="answer5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          You can contact us anytime via the support form (coming soon).  
          We‚Äôre here to help you take great care of your plants üå±.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div> <!-- end accordion -->

</div>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>

</body>
</html>
